Rowan to Spin Off, Sell Manufacturing, Land-Rig Units

-- B y   D a v i d   W e t h e
-- 
2011-02-25T13:27:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-25/rowan-to-spin-off-sell-manufacturing-land-rig-units-correct-.html
(Corrects spelling of CEO’s name in second paragraph.)  Rowan Companies Inc. said
“favorable conditions now exist” for a spinoff or sale of its
manufacturing unit.  The company is also going to begin a process to monetize
its land-rig business, Chief Executive Officer Matthew Ralls
said in a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
